text: Yu Jeong-jae (born 24 November 1970) is a South Korean equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of South Korea Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
